---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { pageMeta } from "../utils/data";

const meta = pageMeta.terms;
const lastUpdated = "6 March 2026";
---

<Layout
  title={meta.title}
  description={meta.description}
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: "Home", href: "/" },
    { name: "Terms & Conditions", href: "/terms" },
  ]}
>
  <article class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1
        class="reveal text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-4"
      >
        Terms &amp; Conditions
      </h1>
      <p class="reveal text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-custom space-y-8">
      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          1. Agreement to Terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          By accessing or using PhantomRank ("the Service"), operated by
          PhantomRank ("we," "us," or "our"), you agree to be bound by these
          Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, do not use the Service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          2. Description of Service
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          PhantomRank is an AI visibility tracking platform that monitors how
          brands are mentioned and cited inside AI-generated answers across
          large language models. The Service is provided on a subscription
          basis with free and paid tiers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          3. Account Registration
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          You must provide accurate, complete information when creating an
          account. You are responsible for maintaining the security of your
          account credentials and for all activity under your account.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          4. Acceptable Use
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
          You agree not to:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground"></span>
            Use the Service to manipulate or spam AI engine outputs
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground"></span>
            Reverse-engineer, decompile, or attempt to extract source code
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground"></span>
            Share account credentials with unauthorised third parties
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground"></span>
            Resell or redistribute data obtained from the Service without written consent
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          5. Payments and Billing
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Paid plans are billed monthly in Indian Rupees (INR). You may upgrade,
          downgrade, or cancel at any time. Downgrades and cancellations take
          effect at the end of the current billing cycle. We do not offer
          refunds for partial billing periods.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          6. Data and Accuracy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          PhantomRank provides AI visibility data on a best-effort basis. AI
          engines change their outputs frequently, and we do not guarantee the
          completeness or accuracy of any scan results. The Service is a
          measurement tool, not a guarantee of AI rankings or placements.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          7. Intellectual Property
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          All content, branding, and technology within PhantomRank remain our
          property. Your data remains yours. We claim no ownership over the
          brand names, content, or information you submit for tracking.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          8. Limitation of Liability
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, PhantomRank shall not be
          liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising
          from your use of the Service. Our total liability shall not exceed
          the fees paid by you in the twelve months preceding the claim.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          9. Termination
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account if you
          violate these Terms. You may delete your account at any time by
          contacting us. Upon termination, your right to access the Service
          ceases immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          10. Changes to Terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          We may update these Terms from time to time. We will notify you of
          material changes via email or through the Service. Continued use
          after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          11. Governing Law
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          These Terms are governed by the laws of India. Any disputes shall
          be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Mumbai,
          Maharashtra.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">
          12. Contact
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          For questions about these Terms, contact us at
          <a
            href="mailto:legal@phantomrank.com"
            class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80"
          >
            legal@phantomrank.com
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
